data.description: Home is located in a serene neighborhood at end of cul de sac street. Fenced back yard overlooks tranquil lake.  Just completed beautiful gourmet kitchen with all new contemporary quartzite countertops, new cabinets, high-end stainless steel appliances, including 3 Italian, Forno ovens. A chef's dream. Expansive living area, with soaring ceilings and large windows, providing magnificent views of spacious lake. In master bedroom, pamper yourself in spa-like ensuite  bathroom, complete with soaking tub, dual vanities  and glass enclosed shower. New tankless water heater. All new wood look tile flooring throughout.Must see beauty!
